_sText:
de_dizzy is a port with remake of the ar_dizzy from the Counter-Strike: Global Offensive game.

The gameplay has been slightly changed on the map. 

There are two zones for planting bombs.

Changed the starting positions of the players.

There is another modified version of this map.

On the server (server address: 46.174.55.204:27015) with the Day of Defeat: Source mod installed, you can play on this map by capturing the flags.

The opposition of the game between the American and Russian teams.
